<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>وَلَوْ سَفَرًا.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- وَلَيْسَتْ شَرْطًا، فَتَصِحُّ مِنْ مُنْفَرِدٍ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- وَلَا يَنْقُصُ أَجْرُهُ مَعَ عُذْرٍ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>- وَتَنْعَقِدُ بِاثْنَيْنِ فِي غَيْرِ جُمُعَةٍ وَعِيدٍ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- وَلَوْ بِأُنْثَى أَوْ عَبْدٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- لَا بِصَبِيٍّ فِي فَرْضٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>- وَحَرُمَ أَنْ يَؤُمَّ بِمَسْجِدٍ لَهُ إِمَامٌ رَاتِبٌ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> فَلَا تَصِحُّ إِلَّا:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١]</span> مَعَ إِذْنِهِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٢]</span> أَوْ عَدَمِ كَرَاهَتِهِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٣]</span> أَوْ تَأَخُّرِهِ وَضِيقِ الوَقْتِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>- وَمَنْ كَبَّرَ قَبْلَ تَسْلِيمَةِ الإِمَامِ الأُولَى؛ أَدْرَكَ الجَمَاعَةَ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- وَمَنْ أَدْرَكَ الرُّكُوعَ أَدْرَكَ الرَّكْعَةَ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>- وَسُنَّ دُخُولُهُ مَعَ إِمَامِهِ كَيْفَ أَدْرَكَهُ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>- وَمَا أَدْرَكَ مَعَهُ آخِرُهَا، وَمَا يَقْضِيهِ أَوَّلُهَا.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَيَتَحَمَّلُ عَنْ مَأْمُومٍ:</span><a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>